{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Synopsis:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> After a yacht disaster, you and your guests are stranded on a mysterious island. Will you fight for survival alone, or work together to keep everyone alive? This game blends romance, survival, base-building, farming, fishing, and pet taming into a unique adventure that challenges your choices and skills in an untamed wilderness.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">           </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">            <strong>Vast Island Map</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore caves, abandoned structures, cliffs, and dense vegetation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Nearly every object is interactable and serves a purpose (e.g., resources, crafting).</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>NPC Relationships</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build bonds through a dynamic affinity system with fully developed characters.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Intelligent NPCs</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">NPCs autonomously eat, cook, rest, gather resources, and fight.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Adapt their behavior based on the player\u2019s actions and needs.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Survival Mechanics</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build shelters, farm crops, incubate and raise pets, and master survival skills.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dynamic Ecosystem</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Diverse creatures/monsters roam specific biomes but engage in combat <i>anywhere</i>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fully open-world exploration with zero restrictions.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Diverse Weaponry</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combat tools: Axes, bows, spears, crossbows, firearms.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Utility tools: Shovels, sickles, bamboo containers.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Seamless Exploration</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Traverse land and dive underwater freely to uncover secrets.</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Important Notes</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Current Status</strong>: The game is in development. Only a <strong>demo version</strong> is available.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Future Plans: Full release will include voice acting and multi-language support.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Apologies</strong>: We appreciate your patience as we refine the experience!</p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2447680?t=1740392248","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2447680/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1740392248","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2447680/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740392248","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2447680/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1740392248","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2605980,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Synopsis:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> After a yacht disaster, you and your guests are stranded on a mysterious island. Will you fight for survival alone, or work together to keep everyone alive? This game blends romance, survival, base-building, farming, fishing, and pet taming into a unique adventure that challenges your choices and skills in an untamed wilderness.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay:</h2><p class=\"bb_parag